NAME
  bang - Bash4 Framework for easy script creation

SYNOPSIS
  bang <command> <arguments>

DESCRIPTION
  This is a set of utility commands to ease bang.sh project creation and development.

BANG COMMANDS

new  creates a new bang project
run  runs a file with the bang environment loaded
test  runs test files of the current's path project

EXAMPLES
  bang run todo.sh

SEE ALSO
  bang-new(1) bang-run(1) bang-test(1)

AUTHOR
